details.description: Visart Cafe offers a variety of coffee drinks, sodas, beer, wine. We also have hot food, charcuterie boards, local pastries and more! The cafe includes a pet friendly garden and access to the Visart theater!

raw_data.name: Visart Cafe
raw_data.description: Visart Cafe offers a variety of coffee drinks, sodas, beer, wine. We also have hot food, charcuterie boards, local pastries and more! The cafe includes a pet friendly garden and access to the Visart theater!

reviews_data.review_text: Had an amazing lavender latte!
The drinks here are always so amazing at such a great price, and the environment is very relaxing.
Lo ame 🥰🥰🥰
Hidden gem with an amazing outdoor garden and delicious coffee. The best part - the ice cubes were made of COFFEE ❤️
Whoa - the grilled cheese sandwich is off the charts delicious as are the baked goods and beverages! And what a fun little patio!!
Great community resource for all things cinema, plus a flourishing flower garden with other local treasures, creating a vibrant and lovely scene.

THEY HAVE COFFEE ICED CUBES, I repeat, COFFEE ice cubes. Best iced coffee I swear… and the vibes are so cute. I feel like I’m back in the 90s/2000s and it makes me incredibly nostalgic and at peace. The empanadas are also fantastic. Also, the garden is beautiful and the running water is so peaceful. This is a must-see in Charlotte! :)

VisArt Café is such a gem! 🎭☕ The service was incredibly friendly, accommodating, and helpful—everyone made me feel welcome. The atmosphere is super cool, with the attached video store and theater space adding a unique, nostalgic vibe.

My food was delicious, and my drink hit the spot. 🍽️🥤 I’m already looking forward to coming back to try more from the menu! The only thing I wish they had were outlets for charging, but honestly, that’s a small detail compared to the overall great experience.

Highly recommend for anyone looking for a cozy, creative space to enjoy good food and good vibes! 🎬✨

review_questions.Seating type: Indoor dining area, Outdoor patio / terrace

reviews_data.review_text: Loved it!
Hours were wrong.

I picked up the vegan chicken salad wrap to take home and it is as good as other reviews say!

Lovely vibe in general. Would love to come back and hang out in the future.

Very cool spot with small bites.
Highly recommend the mozzarella sticks

The coffee is great & I love the brownies

Thank you Visart for your awesome service!
Truly a hidden gem, the patio has such a wonderful garden and it was so nice to sit and read with a coffee for a few hours!
Cute little coffee spot right where I live and the server was patient with me when I was ordering. Will be back again soon.
Such a great vibe!
This cafe has great coffee, a beautiful patio, and fantastic service. I enjoy it every time I come in.

Eine kleine Oase! Die Bedienung ist super nett. Love her smile, Love her style!
Es ist schön schattig und der Kaffee schmeckt super. Danke, dass es euch gibt.
Good vibes all around.  Good ppl food n entertainment
Great unique place!
Wow! The best!

Such a hidden gem in Charlotte! This is the perfect spot for a cute unique date, a client meet up, or just some nice alone time. As long as the cafe is open you can go into the Cinema and enjoy a free movie. We went and they were playing Death Becomes Her so you’re sure to find a classic. Coffee was excellent and reasonable priced. We had two coffees, charcuterie board, and two empanadas for less than $30 total. A steal in this economy!

The best little coffee shop! I love this place more and more every time I visit. The coffee is wonderful, and the frozen coffee they use as ice is so smart and delicious! The empanadas are a must as well as the lemonade. The staff is also wonderful and so very helpful. This morning, I met Aubrey, who was nothing short of the best and so kind. The vibes here are always incredible, especially when the flowers are blooming. So, support small business and get some really tasty coffee here!

It's a really cool place. Good coffee.

The video store in the back made me feel like i was in blockbuster again.
Great outdoor seating area!
Totally addicted to their iced coffee. Great atmosphere. Best courtyard around.
Wow!!! Carry out food from BUTLERS PANTRY!!! Fantastic! ENDERLY COFFEE!! Fantastic!
It’s one of my most favorite places!
We love VisArt Cafe! The staff is awesome! Love the garden! Great place for a meeting during the day or to relax with a glass of wine in the evening.
Love the garden- my dog does too - even in the rain!!
